Title: Counting Coup
Writer: Craig Johnson (book), Hunt Baldwin (developer), John Coveny (developer), Sarah Nicole Jones

Plot: Branch has proof that David Ridges is alive, and Longmire connects him to Jacob Nighthorse. Meanwhile, Sean makes Longmire serve divorce papers to Vic, and Henry faces another setback related to his trial.
